<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Sblood" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">'Sblood,</orth> abbreviated from <emph>God's blood;</emph> a curse apparently thought indecent, and therefore usually omitted or replaced by other words in Ff.: <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.82" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 82</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.3.247" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 247</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.2.37" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.270" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 270</bibl> (Ff <emph>away</emph>). 488 (Ff <emph>i' faith</emph>). <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.56" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.56" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 56</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.4.113" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 113</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.384" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 384</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.386" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 386</bibl> (Ff <emph>why</emph>). <bibl n="shak. oth 1.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 1, 4</bibl>. Found also in Ff: <bibl n="shak. h5 4.8.10" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 8, 10</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>